changelog
V1.1
core Application.php changed to get DB, DBusername, and DB password from master intranet DB based on the $_SERVER['HTTP_HOST'] variable. That way entire intranet can be moved and turned on with no code changes.

moving all DB queries to sql_class.php

******* run these commands to initialize the vagrant box*********
sudo vagrant init centos/7
sudo vagrant up
sudo vagrant ssh
sudo /vagrant/postgres-setup/./second.sh
sudo su - globaluniformuser
gunzip -c /vagrant/php_intranet_uniformsourcing.gz | psql -U globaluniformuser -d php_intranet_uniformsourcing